any freedom at all.

01:18:04.914 --> 01:18:06.047
He, like, froze that lady.

01:18:06.049 --> 01:18:09.483
You know?
Ok, it may look
really cool,

01:18:09.485 --> 01:18:11.552
You know, but...
It isn't.

01:18:11.554 --> 01:18:14.355
In fact, here,
it is the very
antithesis of cool.

01:18:14.357 --> 01:18:17.258
Which, I suppose,
would be uncool.

01:18:17.260 --> 01:18:18.592
I think I understand.

01:18:18.594 --> 01:18:20.478
Oh, righteous!

01:18:20.479 --> 01:18:22.363
So, then, maybe it's time
you stand up to your father?

01:18:22.365 --> 01:18:24.098
