01:20:17.947 --> 01:20:20.815
Hold it right there, gasbag.

01:20:20.817 --> 01:20:23.350
Don't mess with my family, dude.

01:20:23.352 --> 01:20:25.653
No doubt.

01:20:40.169 --> 01:20:45.873
Foolish children,
do not question
my authority!

01:20:54.350 --> 01:20:57.585
